all_EWR %>% 
  filter(delayed == TRUE) %>% 
  mutate(delay_period = case_when(
    dep_delay < 10 ~ "< 10min",
    dep_delay <= 60 ~ "10min - 60min",
    dep_delay > 60 ~ "> 60min"
  )) %>% 
  group_by(delay_period) %>% 
  summarise(n = n()) %>% 
  mutate(percentage = n / sum(n))
month_plot_text <- all_EWR %>% 
  group_by(month, delayed) %>% 
  summarise(n = n()) %>% 
  mutate(delay_percent = round(n / sum(n) * 100)) %>% 
  filter(delayed == TRUE)
